HOW SCARY ARE YOU? 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Imelda awoke from the recurring nightmare: outfits with no matching shoes!  
</P>
<P>
 Think you can come up with a scarier story? 
</P>
<P>
 We invite you to enter the Second Annual Scariest Halloween Story Ever Told 
Contest.You can do it with words (maximum 700) or with a drawing (one page and 
in color). 
</P>
<P>
