 Orange Unified School District 
</P>
<P>
 board meeting 
</P>
<P>
 When: Thursday, 7 p.m. 
</P>
<P>
 Where: Administration Center, 1401 N. Handy St. 
</P>
<P>
 What: The board will discuss whether to contract with a private company, 
Education Alternatives Inc. for some services. The company manages schools in 
Florida, Maryland and Connecticut. 
