COMMUNITY NEWS FOCUS: COUNTYWIDE; HOLIDAY CLOSINGS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Columbus Day will be observed today. The following schedules will be in 
effect: 
</P>
<P>
 * Federal and county offices will be closed. All city offices will open, 
except in Seal Beach, Stanton and Tustin. 
</P>
<P>
 * County, state and federal courthouses will be closed. 
</P>
<P>
 * City and county libraries will be on a regular schedule.  
</P>
<P>
 * Banks will be closed. Savings and loans will be open. 
</P>
<P>
 * Schools, colleges and universities will be open. There will be no classes 
for Huntington Beach schools, Laguna Beach Unified and Westminster elementary 
schools. Call local school districts to confirm. 
</P>
<P>
 * Mail: There will be no postal service. 
</P>
<P>
 * Trash: Trash will be collected on a regular schedule. 
</P>
<P>
 * Buses: OCTA buses will run on a regular schedule. * Parks: All city- and 
county-run parks will be open. 
</P>
