 NOTABLE QUOTE 
</P>
<P>
 "He'll vote when he gets around to it. 
</P>
<P>
 "He hasn't had to fight for it. 
</P>
<P>
 "It's always been there. 
</P>
<P>
 "If there's extra time. Later. Next Year. 
</P>
<P>
 "Later might just be too late." 
</P>
<P>
 -- From the poem "Later," by Carina Joy Bender, a Rio Americano High School 
student in Sacramento, published in the official California ballot pamphlet. 
</P>
